data.description: JUST LOWERED $20,000 AND PAID OFF SOLAR - Offering the best of private desert living from a quality builder, D. R. Horton. This North & South facing  property offers more privacy than the neighbors, boasting hundreds of miles of desert views all the way out to Vulture Mtn from its backyard. As you enter the home you are greeted by a guest bathroom and two spacious guest rooms that sit far from the master bedroom, situated on the other end of the home. As you walk down the hall, the home opens up to you offering a large open layout including the main entertainment space, kitchen, formal dining room and a large sliding glass door to the covered patio. Kitchen features new cabinets, granite and stainless steel appliances. The master offers a large walk-in close The Backyard hots all of the attention with it's breath-taking Saguaro and Vulture mountain views with a nightly sunset performance. There is a large storage shed offering 220V plugs and 30 amps with lighting for any car or shop enthusiast. Custom built viewing deck so that the next owner can enjoy drinks and dinner with friends as they watch the sunset and look out at the desert instead of the side of their neighbors house.
